=== BUILDING ===
To build this program C++ boost library needs to be installed on the system. Also g++ must support C++11 standard.
To build all components, execute:
make all
To clean up after build, execute:
make clean
or to clean binaries as well, execute:
make cleanall



=== EXECUTING ===
To run this program, simply run the following in terminal:
./server 1313

To verify the program works, run multiple times the client programs in separate terminal as follows:
./client localhost 1313 service message
Each message from service is counted on server.

To check number of messages passed to server from each service, type "count" to server terminal.
To quit server type "exit" to server terminal.
